<!doctype html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Atelier Ethos — Mockup V3</title>
  <style>
    /* ============================================================
       ATELIER ETHOS — Mockup V3
       Eski sitenin somut sayılarına sadık + yeni kurallar:
        - Navbar fixed, logo 66px, navbar 90px
        - Sağ üstte: dil toggle + "Etkinlik Takvimi" (kırmızı)
        - "Görüşme Talep Et" SADECE hero ortada + sticky
        - Navbar linki olarak Kaynaklar EKLE, Etkinlikler navbar'da YOK
        - H1 weight 500 (eski siten öyle)
        - Stat sayıları kırmızı, küçük (30px)
        - Cards: rounded 6-8px, border veya gri zemin
        - Bullet: '—' (tire)
        - Section min-height 100vh
       ============================================================ */

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      color: #414042;
      background: #fff;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    em { font-style: normal; color: #c12033; }
    a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }
    button { font-family: inherit; cursor: pointer; }
    ul { list-style: none; }
    img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }

    /* ---------- NAVBAR (fixed, 90px) ---------- */
    .ae-nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
      background: #fff;
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid #e8e8e8;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 12px 60px;
      height: 90px;
    }
    .ae-nav-brand img { height: 66px; width: auto; }

    .ae-nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 28px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .ae-nav-links a {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #414042;
      transition: color 0.15s;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .ae-nav-links a:hover { color: #c12033; }

    .ae-nav-right {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    /* DİL TOGGLE — bizim tasarım dilimizde, sade */
    .ae-lang {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .ae-lang button {
      background: none;
      border: none;
      padding: 4px 6px;
      color: #a7a9ab;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: color 0.15s;
      font-family: inherit;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: inherit;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .ae-lang button.active { color: #414042; }
    .ae-lang button:hover:not(.active) { color: #414042; }
    .ae-lang-sep {
      width: 1px;
      height: 12px;
      background: #e8e8e8;
    }

    /* SAĞ ÜST — Etkinlik Takvimi butonu (küçültülmüş) */
    .ae-nav-cta {
      background: #c12033;
      color: #fff !important;
      font-size: 12px;
      padding: 7px 14px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .ae-nav-cta:hover { background: #a81c2b; }

    /* ---------- SECTION GENERIC ---------- */
    .ae-section {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 110px 60px 60px;
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid #f0f0f0;
    }
    .ae-inner { width: 100%; max-width: 1100px; }

    .ae-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 2.5px;
      color: #c12033;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      display: block;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .ae-h1 {
      font-size: 68px;
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 1.1;
      color: #414042;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .ae-h2 {
      font-size: 38px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #414042;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
    .ae-lead {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #6b6b6b;
      line-height: 1.75;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    /* ---------- HERO ---------- */
    #ae-hero { text-align: center; }
    #ae-hero .ae-inner {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
    #ae-hero .ae-lead { text-align: center; }

    .ae-btns {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .ae-btn-primary {
      background: #c12033;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 15px 32px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 15px;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .ae-btn-primary:hover { background: #a81c2b; }
    .ae-btn-outline {
      border: 1px solid #414042;
      color: #414042;
      padding: 15px 32px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 15px;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .ae-btn-outline:hover {
      border-color: #c12033;
      color: #c12033;
    }

    /* ---------- YAKLAŞIM ---------- */
    .ae-values {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .ae-val {
      background: #f7f7f6;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 24px 28px;
    }
    .ae-val h3 {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #414042;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .ae-val p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b6b6b;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
    .ae-quote {
      border-left: 3px solid #c12033;
      padding: 20px 28px;
      background: #faf9f9;
      border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
    }
    .ae-quote p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #414042;
      line-height: 1.75;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    /* ---------- STATS / GERÇEKLEŞTİRDİKLERİMİZ ---------- */
    .ae-stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .ae-stat { text-align: center; }
    .ae-stat-num {
      font-size: 30px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #c12033;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .ae-stat-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #a7a9ab;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .ae-stat img {
      height: 52px;
      width: auto;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      object-fit: contain;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .ae-referans-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .ae-ref-card {
      border: 0.5px solid #e8e8e8;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 24px 28px;
    }
    .ae-ref-card h3 {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #414042;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
    }
    .ae-ref-card ul li {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #6b6b6b;
      line-height: 1.85;
      padding-left: 16px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .ae-ref-card ul li::before {
      content: '—';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: #c12033;
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    /* ---------- HİZMETLER ---------- */
    .ae-services {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .ae-svc {
      display: flex;
      gap: 24px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      border: 0.5px solid #e8e8e8;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 24px 28px;
    }
    .ae-svc-num {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #ececec;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      width: 40px;
    }
    .ae-svc h3 {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #414042;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .ae-svc ul li {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b6b6b;
      line-height: 1.85;
      padding-left: 16px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .ae-svc ul li::before {
      content: '—';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: #c12033;
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    /* ---------- ETKİNLİKLER (YENİ) — eski sitenin diliyle ---------- */
    .ae-events-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-end;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .ae-events-header > div { flex: 1; min-width: 280px; }
    .ae-events-link {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #c12033;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #c12033;
      padding-bottom: 2px;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }
    .ae-events-link:hover { opacity: 0.7; }

    .ae-events-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .ae-event-card {
      border: 0.5px solid #e8e8e8;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 24px 28px;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .ae-event-card:hover {
      border-color: #c12033;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .ae-event-date {
      display: flex;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      padding-bottom: 14px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
    }
    .ae-event-day {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #c12033;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .ae-event-month {
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      color: #a7a9ab;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .ae-event-type {
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      color: #a7a9ab;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .ae-event-title {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #414042;
      line-height: 1.3;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .ae-event-desc {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #6b6b6b;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .ae-event-cta {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #414042;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #414042;
      padding-bottom: 2px;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .ae-event-card:hover .ae-event-cta {
      color: #c12033;
      border-color: #c12033;
    }

    .ae-events-past-title {
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 2.5px;
      color: #a7a9ab;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding-top: 24px;
      border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
    }
    .ae-past-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .ae-past-card {
      background: #faf9f9;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 18px;
    }
    .ae-past-thumb {
      aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
      background: #ececec;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #a7a9ab;
      position: relative;
    }
    .ae-past-thumb::after {
      content: '▶';
      position: absolute;
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #c12033;
      font-size: 14px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .ae-past-meta {
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      color: #a7a9ab;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .ae-past-title {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #414042;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    /* ---------- KAYNAKLAR (YENİ) — eski sitenin diliyle ---------- */
    .ae-resources-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .ae-resource-card {
      border: 0.5px solid #e8e8e8;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 28px;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      min-height: 240px;
    }
    .ae-resource-card:hover {
      border-color: #c12033;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .ae-resource-num {
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 2.5px;
      color: #c12033;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .ae-resource-title {
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #414042;
      line-height: 1.3;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .ae-resource-desc {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #6b6b6b;
      line-height: 1.7;
      flex: 1;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .ae-resource-count {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #a7a9ab;
      padding-top: 14px;
      border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
    }
    .ae-resources-cta-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    /* ---------- NEDEN BİZ ---------- */
    .ae-why {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .ae-why-card {
      border: 0.5px solid #e8e8e8;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 24px 28px;
    }
    .ae-why-card h3 {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #414042;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .ae-why-card p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b6b6b;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
    .ae-claim {
      background: #f5f5f4;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .ae-claim p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #414042;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }
    .ae-claim strong { color: #c12033; }

    /* ---------- İLETİŞİM ---------- */
    #ae-iletisim { background: #faf9f9; }
    .ae-contact {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 80px;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .ae-contact-info p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #6b6b6b;
      line-height: 1.75;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .ae-contact-detail {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 14px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b6b6b;
    }
    .ae-contact-detail a { color: #c12033; }

    .ae-fg { margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .ae-fg input, .ae-fg textarea {
      width: 100%;
      border: 0.5px solid #d4d4d4;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #414042;
      font-family: inherit;
      outline: none;
      background: #fff;
    }
    .ae-fg input:focus, .ae-fg textarea:focus { border-color: #c12033; }
    .ae-fg textarea { height: 120px; resize: vertical; }
    .ae-submit {
      background: #c12033;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 15px;
      width: 100%;
      font-family: inherit;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .ae-submit:hover { background: #a81c2b; }

    /* ---------- FOOTER ---------- */
    .ae-footer {
      padding: 28px 60px;
      border-top: 0.5px solid #e8e8e8;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .ae-footer-copy { font-size: 13px; color: #a7a9ab; }
    .ae-footer-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; }
    .ae-footer-links a {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #a7a9ab;
      transition: color 0.15s;
    }
    .ae-footer-links a:hover { color: #c12033; }

    /* ---------- STICKY (sağ alt) ---------- */
    .ae-sticky {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 28px;
      right: 28px;
      z-index: 2000;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: flex-end;
    }
    .ae-sticky-cta {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: #c12033;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 14px;
      padding: 13px 22px;
      border-radius: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .ae-sticky-cta:hover { background: #a81c2b; }
    .ae-sticky-up {
      background: #414042;
      color: #fff;
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .ae-sticky-up:hover { background: #2a2a2c; }

    /* ---------- RESPONSIVE ---------- */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .ae-nav { padding: 14px 20px; height: 70px; }
      .ae-nav-brand img { height: 44px; }
      .ae-nav-links { display: none; }
      .ae-section { padding: 90px 20px 40px; min-height: auto; }
      .ae-h1 { font-size: 40px; }
      .ae-h2 { font-size: 28px; }
      .ae-values, .ae-why, .ae-contact, .ae-referans-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .ae-stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .ae-events-grid, .ae-past-grid, .ae-resources-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .ae-footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; text-align: center; }
      .ae-svc { flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- ============ NAVBAR ============ -->
  <nav class="ae-nav">
    <a href="#ae-hero" class="ae-nav-brand">
      <img src="https://atelier-ethos.vercel.app/LogoSS.png" alt="Atelier Ethos" />
    </a>

    <div class="ae-nav-links">
      <a href="#ae-yaklasim">Yaklaşımımız</a>
      <a href="#ae-referanslar">Gerçekleştirdiklerimiz</a>
      <a href="#ae-hizmetler">Hizmetler</a>
      <a href="#ae-kaynaklar">Kaynak Kütüphanesi</a>
      <a href="#ae-neden">Neden Biz?</a>
    </div>

    <div class="ae-nav-right">
      <div class="ae-lang">
        <button class="active">TR</button>
        <span class="ae-lang-sep"></span>
        <button>EN</button>
      </div>
      <a href="#ae-etkinlikler" class="ae-nav-cta">Etkinlik Takvimi</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
  <section id="ae-hero" class="ae-section">
    <div class="ae-inner">
      <span class="ae-label">EST. 2022 · İK Danışmanlık Atölyesi</span>
      <h1 class="ae-h1">İnsanı merkeze alan<br><em>sistemler</em> kuruyoruz.</h1>
      <p class="ae-lead">İşe alımdan performansa, çalışan deneyiminden kültüre — insan altyapısını tam entegre sistem olarak tasarlıyor ve hayata geçiriyoruz.</p>
      <div class="ae-btns">
        <a href="#ae-iletisim" class="ae-btn-primary">Görüşme Talep Et</a>
        <a href="#ae-hizmetler" class="ae-btn-outline">Hizmetlerimiz</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ YAKLAŞIM ============ -->
  <section id="ae-yaklasim" class="ae-section">
    <div class="ae-inner">
      <span class="ae-label">Yaklaşımımız</span>
      <h2 class="ae-h2">Bir İK atölyesiyiz</h2>
      <p class="ae-lead">Organizasyonunuzda başarmak istediğiniz hedefleri atölyemize alıyor, sizinle birlikte projelendiriyoruz.</p>

      <div class="ae-values">
        <div class="ae-val">
          <h3>Çevik</h3>
          <p>Değişime ve büyümeye hızlı uyum sağlayan, krizlere karşı dirençli yapılar.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ae-val">
          <h3>Adaptatif</h3>
          <p>Değişime ve büyümeye hızlı uyum sağlayan süreçler.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ae-val">
          <h3>Öngörülebilir</h3>
          <p>Veriye dayalı, tahmin edilebilir operasyonel çıktılar.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ae-val">
          <h3>Aidiyetli</h3>
          <p>Kurum kültürüyle bütünleşmiş, bağlılığı yüksek ekipler.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ae-quote">
        <p>İK departmanınızın doğal bir uzantısı gibi, bilfiil projeleri birlikte yapıyoruz. Süreç tasarımı, atölye programları, dijital araçlar — hedefe ulaşmak için ne gerekiyorsa, birlikte hayata geçiriyoruz.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ GERÇEKLEŞTİRDİKLERİMİZ ============ -->
  <section id="ae-referanslar" class="ae-section">
    <div class="ae-inner">
